"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"At least five children were reportedly killed in the strike, which seems to have targeted a Hamas commander. Neither side seems interested in a return to full conflict, despite the latest exchange of strikes.\",            \"english_title\": \"Strike Kills Children\",            \"translated_version\": \"Al menos cinco ni\u00f1os murieron en el ataque, que parece haber apuntado a un comandante de Hamas. Ning\u00fan lado parece querer volver a un conflicto total, a pesar del \u00faltimo intercambio de ataques.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ataque Mata Ni\u00f1os\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The case is about whether the former columnist lied about the money she got for her civil lawsuit against the US president.\",            \"english_title\": \"Columnist's Lawsuit\",            \"translated_version\": \"El caso es sobre si la ex columnista minti\u00f3 sobre el dinero que recibi\u00f3 por su demanda civil contra el presidente de EE.UU.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Demanda de Columnista\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The hostilities come during a fragile ceasefire between the US and Iran, and long negotiations to end the three-month war. Beirut had until now largely been spared even as both Israel and Hezbollah accused each other of breaking last month's ceasefire.\",            \"english_title\": \"Fragile Ceasefire\",            \"translated_version\": \"Las hostilidades ocurren durante un fr\u00e1gil alto el fuego entre EE.UU. e Ir\u00e1n, y largas negociaciones para terminar la guerra de tres meses. Beirut hasta ahora hab\u00eda estado en gran parte a salvo, aunque Israel y Hezbollah se acusaron mutuamente de romper el alto el fuego del mes pasado.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Alto el Fuego Fr\u00e1gil\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Police say the operation targeted the network of the notorious late Sicilian mafia boss Matteo Messina Denaro. A 31-year-old Swiss man has been arrested, police say, as images from the scene show parts of the station blocked off.\",            \"english_title\": \"Mafia Network Operation\",            \"translated_version\": \"La polic\u00eda dice que la operaci\u00f3n apunt\u00f3 a la red del famoso jefe de la mafia siciliana Matteo Messina Denaro. Un suizo de 31 a\u00f1os ha sido arrestado, dice la polic\u00eda, mientras im\u00e1genes del lugar muestran partes de la estaci\u00f3n bloqueadas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Operaci\u00f3n Red Mafia\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The European Commission says the Chinese-owned online retailer did not consider the risks from baby toys and faulty chargers sold on its platform.\",            \"english_title\": \"Retailer Safety Concerns\",            \"translated_version\": \"La Comisi\u00f3n Europea dice que el minorista en l\u00ednea de propiedad china no consider\u00f3 los riesgos de los juguetes para beb\u00e9s y cargadores defectuosos vendidos en su plataforma.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Preocupaciones de Seguridad del Minorista\"        }    ]}"